parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as well as cause damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: airbags fail to deploy in an accident

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the Takata airbag recall can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as well as cause frustration and inconvenience to vehicle owners.
symptoms: lack of communication from the manufacturer
and continued exposure to the risk of airbag failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cracking of the dashboard can cause airbag deployment issues, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: particularly around the passenger airbag area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and fragmentation of the dashboard can lead to sharp edges and pointed objects that can cause injuries to occupants in the event of an accident. Additionally, the cracked dashboard can compromise the structural integrity of the airbag system, potentially leading to malfunction or failure.
symptoms: cracks extending from the airbag area
cracks on the passenger side airbag area
and crumbling of the dashboard material.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and disintegration of the dashboard can cause flying plastic projectiles in the event of an accident, which can lead to serious injury or even death.
symptoms: cracks on the driver's side and passenger side of the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the trunk lid can cause injury or accidents, especially if it slams shut while someone is trying to access the trunk.
